ir and capture Merry and Pippin. Aragorn, Gimli and Legolas debate which pair of hobbits to follow.;10:Lord of the Rings #3 - The Return of the King:J. R. R. Tolkien:Sauron sends a great army against Gondor. Gandalf arrives at Minas Tirith to warn Denethor of the attack, while Th?oden musters the Rohirrim to ride to Gondor's aid.